TO RUN PACKAGE WITH MULTIPLE CLASSES USE FOLLOWING -->

D:\>javac -d pkg_test emp.java

D:\>javac -d pkg_test emp1.java

D:\>javac -d pkg_test emp2.java

D:\>cd pkg_test

D:\pkg_test>javac employee.java

D:\pkg_test>java employee
we are in pkg1 class emp
emp id=110
basic=10000
exit from class emp
we are in pkg1 class emp1
emp id=220
basic=5000
exit from class emp1
we are in pkg1 class emp2
emp id=330
basic=20000
exit from class emp2

D:\pkg_test>